                    <h4 class="text-blue-500 mb-2">@someUserName</h4>
                    <p class="tracking-tight text-sm">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fuga libero ipsa reiciendis delectus enim, minus laudantium itaque dolores deserunt, labore ea neque id odit eius molestiae cupiditate inventore cum facilis?</p>
                    <div class="btns flex gap-4 mt-3">
                        <a class="text-blue-500" href="">Like</a>
                        <a class="text-zinc-500" href="">Edit</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
